    <ul>
      <li><strong>Financial Independence:</strong> Let your money work for you, so you can spend more time with your loved ones.</li>
      <li><strong>Freedom to Explore:</strong> Follow God’s call to serve others, travel the world, or simply enjoy life with your family.</li>
      <li><strong>Future Security:</strong> Build a solid foundation for your family and find peace knowing you’ve prepared for the future.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section id="explore-topics">
    <h2>Explore Topics That Help You Take Action</h2>
    <div class="articles-grid">
      <article>
        <h3>Getting Started with Affiliate Marketing</h3>
        <p>Earn passive income by sharing products you love and trust. Let your efforts work for you, even while you sleep!</p>
        <a href="affiliate-marketing.html" class="read-more">Read More</a>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h3>Create and Sell Digital Products</h3>
        <p>Use your God-given talents to create e-books, online courses, or templates. Share your gifts with the world while creating a sustainable income.</p>
        <a href="digital-products.html" class="read-more">Read More</a>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h3>Investing in Income-Generating Assets</h3>
        <p>Put your money into stocks, real estate, or other assets that bring consistent returns. Build wealth while trusting God’s provision.</p>
        <a href="investing-assets.html" class="read-more">Read More</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="testimonials">
    <h2>What Our Readers Say</h2>
    <blockquote>
      <p>"This blog helped me create my first online course and earn while spending more time with my kids!"</p>
      <cite>– Sarah, Digital Nomad</cite>
    </blockquote>
    <blockquote>
      <p>"I didn’t think I could do it, but with this guide, I earned my first $1,000 through affiliate marketing. Praise God!"</p>
      <cite>– Mike, Side Hustler</cite>
    </blockquote>
  </section>

  <section id="newsletter">
    <h2>Join the Journey</h2>
    <p>Stay inspired and keep learning. Sign up for our newsletter to get exclusive tips and updates on the best passive income strategies – straight to your inbox.</p>
    <form>
      <input type="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required>
      <button type="submit" class="cta-button">Subscribe Now</button>
    </form>
  </section>

